<%- include("partials/head", { title: "Home Bar QR Menu" }) %>

<section class="hero">
  <h1>Meniu de cocktail-uri cu QR</h1>
  <p>
    Prietenii scaneaza QR-ul, vad bauturile (poza + nume + ingrediente) si pot trimite comanda direct pe WhatsApp.
  </p>
  <div class="hero-actions">
    <a class="btn" href="/menu">Deschide meniul</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="qr-section card">
  <h2>Scaneaza acest cod</h2>
  <img class="qr-image" src="/qr.png" alt="Cocktail menu QR code" />
  <p class="mono"><%= menuUrl %></p>
  <p>Poti printa codul si sa-l pui pe masa sau langa bar.</p>
  <% if (!whatsappConfigured) { %>
    <p class="alert">Seteaza `WHATSAPP_NUMBER` in `.env` ca sa functioneze trimiterea comenzilor pe WhatsApp.</p>
  <% } %>
</section>

<%- include("partials/foot") %>
